#String tooltip
Bot burns garden pots in kilns. You need to specify an area that has unburnt pots in the 'Take' section. You also need to specify an area with specialisation 'kilns'. You need to specify the area with specialisation 'fuel(branch)'' and the area where to put ready pots with specialisation 'gardenpot'. A candelabra with a candle is used for ignition.